name: HungryWoof
0:
”Alexa, ask hungry woof to make a new log”
”Alexa, ask hungry woof to check last log”
”Alexa, ask hungry woof to make new log for two p. m. today”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: hungry woof
des:
Keeping your pet properly fed is a very important task and sometimes if not often you might forget when was the last time he/she ate, Hungry woof keeps a log for the last time you fed your pet and can make new log at your command . You wont have to remember when was the last time your pet ate food because you now have hungry woof. 
There are many cases of over eating among pets which eventually make them obese or it sometimes even proves to be fatal. All of this can be avoided by this simple yet effective skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
